title: 2 Story 1bed/1bath Condo in Great Location- 786 Minna 6
posting_body: ['Capture The Charm, Love The Space, Live The Location', 'Make this spacious 2 level condo your home!', 'Light-filled, it includes a spacious open living room/dining room/kitchen with a working gas fireplace.', "The chef's kitchen has top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, wood cabinets, gas range, microwave, dishwasher, disposal, refrigerator.", 'Upstairs is a large bedroom with a huge walk-in closet and beautifully renovated bathroom with roomie shower and double sink.', 'Condo comes with parking and storage.', 'Located in the trendy heart of SOMA.', 'Close to Downtown, Civic Center, BART and MUNI, the Opera, Symphony, Westfield Shopping Center, and numerous hip dining spots such as AQ Restaurant, 54 Mint.', 'PLUS Easy access to 280, 101, 80, and public transportation!', " Be prepared for 'love at first sight'.", 'See this one quickly or miss a great home.', '** Tenant pays for electricity and gas', '** Tenant(s) will be responsible for following any HOA-mandated “Rules & Responsibilities” and “Covenants, Conditions & Restrictions.”', '**', '** Tenant is responsible for any HOA Move in/Move out fees if applicable**', '** Security Deposit is equal to 1x the monthly rent based upon approved credit.', '(NOTE: In CA, can increase security deposits to 2x rent.', 'Please see the statement of rental criteria here: <URL>', '**', 'If you are interested in applying, please email', 'show contact info', 'or text', 'show contact info', 'to request an application.', 'Please note that applications are reviewed in the order received and application fees are not refundable.', '**']
